Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.03,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.68,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:33.83,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Are you okay, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:37.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of got dizzy as I was \Ngoing through the steps...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.88,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How did she end up being the heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.26,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a better actor, \Nand my face is cuter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.26,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:45.61,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:21.99,sign_3285_14_A_Kind_Girl_Who_,Title,0000,0000,0000,,A Kind Girl Who Isn't Kind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:27.71,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.68,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.42,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:35.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hot after all that practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you're wearing \Nthat practice outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.46,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one I lent you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:00.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's really comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It breathes well, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:11.08,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you really \Ndo have remarkable proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.83,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I asked you to be the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do to try any harder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.37,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now we'll work \Non the steps for part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.35,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Three, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.42,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.01,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her? \NShe can't even get this down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:44.83,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.83,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How can she play the heroine \Nif she can't master something this basic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.11,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you do this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:53.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If you just stay relaxed, you'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:06.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:11.54,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Chiaki-senpai won't \Nlook at anyone but that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:16.70,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I respect Chiaki-senpai \Nso much more than she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.70,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, once more from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Three, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:20.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.03,Main Dialogue,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.83,Main Dialogue,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine! This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I just slipped a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.17,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chiaki-senpai is looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.80,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to the nurse's office,\N just to be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:46.42,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do? I have to answer her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.80,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm all choked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.31,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.24,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I only just became friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:03.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud, \Nstop shaking me! You'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to leave early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I can practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:18.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Just try not to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.18,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That will be all for our group practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.42,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,You should all practice on your own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.22,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.97,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work harder so Chiaki-senpai \Nwill recognize my abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to practice with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:43.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be more fun \Nif we practiced together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:47.86,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... There's me and Kuu-chan and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.86,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why should I practice with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And the landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:54.39,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, fine, then. But just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.41,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Like this... and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:08.63,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And for the next step, do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.21,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,When I see her up close like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.14,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,she's actually pretty devoted to learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.84,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And then this... And next...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.84,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's clumsy, but at least she's eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.60,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! Are you okay, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.14,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.53,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.04,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.25,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're... doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.12,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.17,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:55.05,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... She may be eager, \Nbut she's still a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.97,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.27,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Today's practice was just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Today was really fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to practice with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.37,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you "Why not?" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all banged up after all the times \Nyou knocked me over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.26,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I admit that you're eager—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:36.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for lending me \Nyour practice outfit today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I got sweaty, so I'll wash it \Nbefore I return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:47.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's old, but you can keep it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:56.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to approve of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.96,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do for the cultural fair? \NA café? Food stall? Or there's always the classic haunted house.\N{\c&HB8255A&}A haunted house? Like this?\N{\c&H7C6055&}...I wonder what'd be best.\NWe have to all think of something by tomorrow...\N{\c&H7CBE7F&}If it involves food, will there be rice balls?\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}Hmm... What will be best?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.96,Note - Copy - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAFAE19&}What are we going to display? Like photos?\N{\c&H7C6055&}If we do a display, it'll be easy but it's sort of lonely...\NThen again, if we do a café, the preparations will be hard... \NActually, everything will be hard.\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}I wonder what kind of café... A maid café?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.02,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to clean the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.10,sign_12015_142_Beginning_Theate,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Beginning Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A theater book?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It has all kinds of different \Npractice methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a way to practice \Nby becoming animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Would a bird look something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Or this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Or how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.26,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, how's the cleaning... going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.26,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is that self-defense training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.72,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, just imitating a bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you imitating a bird, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:14.53,sign_13062_159_Beginning_Theate,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My movements are too stiff,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I always bump into people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.53,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't a bird look more like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like you're actually going to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:35.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.71,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.55,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you guys in the middle of cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So you were imitating animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We practice that way in the \Ntheater club sometimes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It broadens your range of expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give us a demonstration, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.10,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:13.59,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,For example, a cat would look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,A dog would look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:23.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You mimic their behaviors and try to \Ncapture their unique characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this seem \Njust the slightest bit erotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, why don't you \Ntry imitating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.97,Main Dialogue,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:39.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you imitate a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's sure to be adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Was this a quiz of some kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:58.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no! That's what \Nrabbits really sound like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.14,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbits sound like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They make that noise \Nwhen they attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,But that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:14.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some animals have cute faces, \Nbut are actually vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:17.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Na guard dog my family used to have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,had a cute face, but a really scary bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.09,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, try imitating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I can get it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.29,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but you said it was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.43,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What was that an imitation of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It was the dog leaping at an intruder \Nand saying, "I'll kill you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't keep any pets here in the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Shop pets are popular these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of animals \Nwere around in your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:04.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs, rabbits, monkeys, tanuki, deer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:11.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been perfect if there were \Nbears and wild boars, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that would go \Nover well at this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.53,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,They seem a bit vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:19.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, they taste really good in hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You keep them \Non the premise of eating them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:27.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That... seems kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.60,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,...tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:35.08,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen all different kinds \Nof real animals, huh, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:35.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not try to recall them \Nwhile you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Animals from the countryside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:42.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Animals from the countryside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so how was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was good. You seemed to be \Nsoaring like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.27,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:21.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! You think I can perform at Suzuran now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.28,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's jumping the gun a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.78,sign_19260_236_Used_Bookstore_H,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've heard \Nshe lives at a used bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Pen, pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.87,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Pen, pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.72,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Pen, pen, pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:48.93,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Pen, pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.77,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's one week left \Nuntil the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.77,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We've got all of our costumes \Nand props together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.53,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing I'm concerned about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:11.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Keep your eyes forward during practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:14.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep that up, I'll never \Napprove of you as the heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.46,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.60,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan's movements are \Nstill as stiff as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.60,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get my acting \Nright today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Yua-chan hates me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how you can stop bumping into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.56,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe by just looking around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:43.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't seem to see anything \Naround me when I'm focused on acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But when I become conscious \Nof my surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get nervous and become a scarecrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How about squinting while you act
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you're only \Nsomewhat aware of your surroundings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That would take both my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about wearing a cute mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That would hide my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, I'll practice with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:09.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.55,sign_19260_236_Used_Bookstore_H,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.55,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:19.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Have you been \Npracticing for the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you practice at the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.30,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! She can never play \Nthe heroine at that rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.20,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to tell her—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.05,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna feed the ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:42.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! There's lots of room, so I can \Npractice without bumping into anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:47.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, were you practicing \Ndancing earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:53.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I think it'd be best \Nfor you to learn from Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:59.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She always practices so she \Ncan dance with a prince someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.64,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell people that! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're really small and cute, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You could get a princess role easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:12.99,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,A-As far as that goes, \Nyou're cute, too, Hina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd step on the prince's feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.12,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or trip and end up tackling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.12,sign_23476_295_Prince_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.12,sign_23502_296_Prince_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.41,sign_23524_297_Prince_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:24.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a fighting competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I need to learn how to dance \Nwithout bumping into people soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.14,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe you should try to be \Nmore aware of your center of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.31,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Center of gravity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.89,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,They're practicing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.89,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right, center of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like if you put something on your head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,and try to walk without dropping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.91,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same posture I'm in \Nwhen I become a scarecrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:06.67,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought my talent \Nas a scarecrow would come in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.17,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did being complimented \Nmake you so happy, you had to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think the dancing should work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any advice for her, Aki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anything she can use to improve her acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.31,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.81,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Being used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:33.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, is there anything she can \Nkeep in mind when she's on the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:38.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Maybe to take advantage of \Nthe pauses left by your co-actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get the hang \Nof reading their pauses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.58,sign_25543_324_Something__Like_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Something\N Like a \NGenius
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:51.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why don't we start \Nby going over your lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.71,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You can't act if you don't know your lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit more confident about my lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been reading the script \Nwith Toritarou every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:09.67,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, can you act out the heroine's part \Nin the beginning of the first chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:17.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I once had someone important \Nthat I wished to protect—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong? "Someone precious"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:26.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I once had someone precious \Nthat I wished to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:31.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This person was more precious \Nto me than my own life—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one is "important"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:39.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This person was more important \Nto me than my own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.85,Italics Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of crazy cheat skill is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and was irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:46.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five years since that person died—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.48,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ready to head back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I want to practice \Njust a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:02.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to conquer my stage fright \Nwith this play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change so I won't be\N a failshrimp anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.25,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep working just a bit longer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:51.47,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,When all is said and done, she's serious \Nabout this. I just can't hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I've got the basics \Nof the dancing down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I've memorized all the lines \Nthrough the first chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I still have more work to do on acting, \Nquick changing, voice projection,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and some other important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm better than I was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I think this might work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:14.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually think you'll be ready \Nfor the culture festival at this rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to mess up \Nany play that I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just train you personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:24.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make this play a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that! \NLet's do this, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.92,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7C1CD2&}I can't do it!\NI can't reach!\N{\c&H7C6055&}-Prefixes and suffixes\N-A prefix is an affix placed in front of a word to modify its meaning. \Nex) "ex" (outside) in express, and "inter" (between) in interview.\N-A suffix is a morpheme added at the end of a word to form a derivative. \Nex) "ish" in boyish (making it an adjective)\N-Prefixes that express numbers. \N-uni = 1. Examples) uniform = uni+form->"one piece of clothing"\Nunicycle = uni+cycle->"unicycle" | universe = uni+verse->"Space, the whole world"\N-multi = many Examples) multinational = multi+national->"many countries"\Nmultipurpose = multi+purpose->"many uses"\Nmedia = multi + media->"multimedia, using various forms of media"\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.92,Note - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7C1CD2&}Gulp, gulp \N Dribble, dribble, dribble\N{\c&H7C6055&}-Question: Circle the correct word for the following definitions.\N1: Impossible to do: A) able B) unable C) enable\N2: A vehicle with three wheels: A) bicycle B) tricycle C) unicycle\N-Suffixes that create adjectives:\N- -ful: <verb or noun + ful> turns it into an adjective meaning "filled with [word]"!\NExamples) powerful = power+ful->"powerful, strong" \N hopeful = hopeful = hope+ful->"filled with hope"\N-If you add -ful to a container noun, it becomes a noun indicating "1 (container) worth."\NExamples) glassful "1 glass worth" | spoonful "1 spoon worth" | saucerful "1 saucer worth"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:46.06,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Practice with Yua-chan was really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.18,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My whole body hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can still keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got a lot to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you keeling over on me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! I'll try my best \Nwith you, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... W-Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:18.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you hated me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're really kind, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the play! Only for the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you? I won't allow mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll keep working my very hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.61,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.64,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Yua-chan and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:32.01,sign_33687_393_Maids__Ghosts__a,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Maids, Ghosts, and the Stage of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:28.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, you're such a handful, it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:30.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But you're serious about this, \Nand you're eager, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to admit that much, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:34.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:37.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show 'em everything I taught you, \Nand leave nothing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:40.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Maids, Ghosts, \Nand the Stage of Dreams."
